  "id": "RAW_c8456cfd",
  "title": "刘润：2026 年，中小企业有个大机会",
  "url": "https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MjM5NjM5MjQ4MQ==&mid=2651782317&idx=1&sn=fa8db1ca7fa506ef316366baeefdaffd",
  "date": "2026-03-22 03:18:00",
  "author": "刘润",
  "siteName": "刘润",
  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <p><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-aistatus=\"1\" data-croporisrc=\"https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/FjoOAxHlyhyudibJnR8A6HaHTT5vbs4Vibhla8e7wQqY65wNnEfJ9EvqYdM7nbA3d3Z1teCafaFQlJggVfbibBxmFaVqT0VIAf0jqWyKM6GnfY/0?wx_fmt=png&amp;from=appmsg\" data-cropselx2=\"578\" data-cropsely2=\"182\" data-imgfileid=\"504298559\" data-ratio=\"0.31443298969072164\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"970\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=d52137d9&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FFjoOAxHlyhyudibJnR8A6HaHTT5vbs4Vibhla8e7wQqY65wNnEfJ9EvqYdM7nbA3d3Z1teCafaFQlJggVfbibBxmFaVqT0VIAf0jqWyKM6GnfY%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\" style=\"font-size: 1rem; text-align: center; width: 100%;\"></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-bottom: 0px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.061855670103092786\" data-type=\"gif\" data-w=\"970\" style=\"width: 100%;\" type=\"block\" data-backw=\"578\" data-backh=\"36\" data-imgfileid=\"504298467\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=926dab5f&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_gif%2FFjoOAxHlyhy86I5OTxhyHMrXk3Z376dpUpicvDzicltRU1hTwKfBeV2DMQ5YbUoy93t2JLD6mLbN0RH3INsW6wOSXicHyerlsswvYRrkT7Wia90%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dgif%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p class=\"channels_iframe_wrp\" nodeleaf=\"\"><mp-common-videosnap class=\"js_uneditable custom_select_card channels_live_iframe\" data-pluginname=\"mpvideosnap\" data-headimgurl=\"https://wx.qlogo.cn/finderhead/ufVMVgCvafJk743y9cyiaUYK0YCC5bpZrsgAkYbl35F2iclOyX6OCENQ/0\" data-username=\"v2_060000231003b20faec8c6e78e1ccad0cd0ceb35b077d3d947c0becfa99d85ad6e1672a2b492@finder\" data-nickname=\"刘润\" data-desc=\"将在03月24日 19:00 直播\" data-type=\"live\" data-intro=\"刘润：从进化岛和古巴带回的新思考\" data-noticeid=\"finderlivenotice-v2_060000231003b20faec8c6e78e1ccad0cd0ceb35b077d3d947c0becfa99d85ad6e1672a2b492@finder-1771759747758412-2124285209\" data-status=\"0\"></mp-common-videosnap></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"margin-bottom: 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span data-eleid=\"3\" style=\"white-space: pre-wrap;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:15px;\">这段时间，我有</span></span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"line-height: 1.75em;white-space: pre-wrap;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:15px;\">种隐隐约约的</span></span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:15px;\">感觉。2026年，中小企业有个大机会。那就是：AI编程。</span></span></span></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"margin-bottom: 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span data-eleid=\"5\" style=\"white-space: pre-wrap;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">先给你讲三个故事。</span></span></span></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"margin-bottom: 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span data-eleid=\"7\" style=\"line-height: 1.75em;white-space: pre-wrap;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"line-height: 1.75em;white-space: pre-wrap;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:15px;\">第一个故事，关于X。一位做制造业的创业者。</span></span></span></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"margin-bottom: 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span data-eleid=\"9\" style=\"white-space: pre-wrap;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">在问道加拉帕戈斯途中，她一直和我抱怨。因为业务的发展，他们的ERP系统需要升级。提出需求后，开发商说这个做不了，那个做不了。能做的那部分，要花很多钱。而且，几个月到一年才能做完。</span></span></span></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"margin-bottom: 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span data-eleid=\"11\" style=\"white-space: pre-wrap;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">她一怒之下，说你把源代码给我，我找人自己重做。他们说，好啊。然后报了个天价。一个中小企业，哪有那么多钱。她进也不是，退也不是。感觉被绑架了。</span></span></span></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"margin-bottom: 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span data-eleid=\"13\" style=\"white-space: pre-wrap;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">我说，要不我们用“AI编程”试试？</span></span></span></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"margin-bottom: 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span data-eleid=\"15\" style=\"white-space: pre-wrap;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">然后，我教她在VSCode里，用Codex分析她（编译好，没有源代码）的ERP客户端。看看能找出点什么。</span></span></span></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"margin-bottom: 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span data-eleid=\"17\" style=\"white-space: pre-wrap;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">Codex说：报告，我发现上一个开发商居然把数据库的管理密码，写死在了客户端里。我用这个密码，连上了数据库。发现里面有300多张表。通过这些表之间的关系，我分析出了你的业务逻辑。如果你愿意，我把所有数据都下载下来，然后帮你写个新的ERP？</span></span></span></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"margin-bottom: 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span data-eleid=\"19\" style=\"white-space: pre-wrap;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">这位创业者惊呆在了当场。</span></span></span></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"margin-bottom: 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span data-eleid=\"21\" style=\"white-space: pre-wrap;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">然后，在加拉帕戈斯船上的那几天，只要不是登岛看蓝脚鲣鸟和海鬣蜥，她就一直在用Codex调试她的ERP。各种她想做，但开发商（不屑地）说做不了的功能，她基本都做出来了。甚至，还做个中文、越南文双语版。</span></span></span></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"margin-bottom: 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span data-eleid=\"23\" style=\"white-space: pre-wrap;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">下船的时候，她双脚踩上陆地上，仿佛一个被绑架了很久的人，重获自由。</span></span></span></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"margin-bottom: 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span data-eleid=\"25\" style=\"line-height: 1.75em;white-space: pre-wrap;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"line-height: 1.75em;white-space: pre-wrap;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:15px;\">第二个故事，关于Z。一位服装外贸行业的创业者。</span></span></span></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"margin-bottom: 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span data-eleid=\"27\" style=\"white-space: pre-wrap;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">她来自全球的客户，会发一个PPT格式，或者PDF格式的服装工艺说明书。请他们按说明生产。</span></span></span></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"margin-bottom: 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span data-eleid=\"29\" style=\"white-space: pre-wrap;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">然后，她需要把这些英语的、西班牙语的、各国语言的文件，对照着图翻译成中文，再请老师傅把它翻译成BOM清单，录入系统，开始排产。</span></span></span></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"margin-bottom: 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span data-eleid=\"31\" style=\"white-space: pre-wrap;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">他们的生意做的不小。所以做这个工序的员工，有40-50人。成本很高。更重要的是，效率比较低。</span></span></span></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"margin-bottom: 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span data-eleid=\"33\" style=\"white-space: pre-wrap;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">所以，她很想做一个翻译并录入的软件。但不知道怎么做。找人来做。又是几十、上百万的报价，和一期二期三期，将近一年的开发周期。</span></span></span></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"margin-bottom: 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span data-eleid=\"35\" style=\"white-space: pre-wrap;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">她说，她有一种“文科生的无力感”。财务、人事都还懂点。可是一涉及到IT，就两眼一抹黑。总觉得不对，但也不知道哪里不对。只能跌跌撞撞前行。</span></span></span></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"margin-bottom: 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span data-eleid=\"37\" style=\"white-space: pre-wrap;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">我说，我帮你，哦不，我请“AI编程”来帮你写个雏形吧。</span></span></span></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"margin-bottom: 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span data-eleid=\"39\" style=\"white-space: pre-wrap;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">你这个翻译最难的，是有专业术语。AI翻译也会经常出错。我帮你接上AI，并且写个“术语对照表”。人机协作一个月，翻译基本就会很准了。</span></span></span></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"margin-bottom: 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span data-eleid=\"41\" style=\"white-space: pre-wrap;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">一天之后，她拿U盘拷贝走了这个翻译软件。然后开始和我讨论她其他的业务逻辑。</span></span></span></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"margin-bottom: 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span data-eleid=\"43\" style=\"white-space: pre-wrap;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">我说，这是雏形。回去还要改改。她说，已经马上回去就能用了。终于有种大口呼吸新鲜空气的感觉了。</span></span></span></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"margin-bottom: 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span data-eleid=\"45\" style=\"line-height: 1.75em;white-space: pre-wrap;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"line-height: 1.75em;white-space: pre-wrap;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:15px;\">第三个故事，关于W。一位在线教育的创业者。</span></span></span></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"margin-bottom: 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span data-eleid=\"47\" style=\"white-space: pre-wrap;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">我们从加拉帕戈斯，回基多机场，等待飞古巴的间隙，他和我讨论他的业务。</span></span></span></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"margin-bottom: 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span data-eleid=\"49\" style=\"white-space: pre-wrap;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">他们的业务严重依赖SaaS系统。但是，过去的SaaS系统，开发的太早了。用的开发语言、技术架构，数据库设计，都有点跟不上了。所以，想找人重新开发。</span></span></span></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"margin-bottom: 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span data-eleid=\"51\" style=\"white-space: pre-wrap;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">新团队看了一下，说以前的源代码很不规范。要彻底补全文档，才能评估怎么是不是能迁移，怎么迁移。于是，他们开始补文档。已经补了两个月了。花了几十万。</span></span></span></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"margin-bottom: 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span data-eleid=\"53\" style=\"white-space: pre-wrap;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">我说，你把让IT负责人，把源代码和数据库结构发过来。</span></span></span></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"margin-bottom: 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span data-eleid=\"55\" style=\"white-space: pre-wrap;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">老板要源代码？下面同事很紧张。很快，我们在机场收到了所有材料。整理的非常清楚。</span></span></span></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"margin-bottom: 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span data-eleid=\"57\" style=\"white-space: pre-wrap;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">然后，我教他用Claude Code，根据源代码和数据库结构，设计全新的架构方案。</span></span></span></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"margin-bottom: 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span data-eleid=\"59\" style=\"white-space: pre-wrap;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">他看着Claude Code给的建议，大惊失色。这和他们几个月讨论下来的方案，大方向基本一致，还考虑到了更多细节和风险。</span></span></span></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"margin-bottom: 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span data-eleid=\"61\" style=\"white-space: pre-wrap;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">之后在古巴的一个星期，他几乎每天都凌晨1-2点睡觉。开始优化方案，甚至自己写原型。一种从未有过的通透感，和对业务的掌控感。</span></span></span></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"margin-bottom: 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span data-eleid=\"63\" style=\"white-space: pre-wrap;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">三个故事讲完了。</span></span></span></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"margin-bottom: 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span data-eleid=\"65\" style=\"white-space: pre-wrap;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">为什么要讲这三个故事？</span></span></span></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"margin-bottom: 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span data-eleid=\"67\" style=\"white-space: pre-wrap;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">因为看着这三位创业者兴奋的表情，我似乎意识到，2026年，AI对中小企业的价值，可能不在那个似乎无所不知的“聊天窗口”里，而在那些总是差点意思的“信息系统”里。</span></span></span></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"margin-bottom: 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span data-eleid=\"69\" style=\"line-height: 1.75em;white-space: pre-wrap;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"line-height: 1.75em;white-space: pre-wrap;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:15px;\">而“差点意思”的原因，就是因为从业务需求到信息系统中的三层摩擦：产品经理，架构师，和程序员。</span></span></span></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"margin-bottom: 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span data-eleid=\"71\" style=\"white-space: pre-wrap;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">产品经理的工作，是把业务需求，翻译成产品逻辑。数据怎么存储，流程怎么流转，界面怎么交互。</span></span></span></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"margin-bottom: 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span data-eleid=\"73\" style=\"white-space: pre-wrap;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">但是，产品经理的水平，非常受限于他的经验，知识面，和学习能力。</span></span></span></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"margin-bottom: 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span data-eleid=\"75\" style=\"white-space: pre-wrap;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">你说，我要加个特殊情况监控。他想不到用“箱线图”分析。你说，我要一个在PPT上直接标注，他说你不懂技术，这个实现不了。</span></span></span></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"margin-bottom: 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span data-eleid=\"77\" style=\"white-space: pre-wrap;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">所以，你一边妥协，一边怪自己大学时没考个高级程序员，不然就不会提出这么愚蠢的需求了。但其实，这些都能做到，只是被他的知识边界，给“摩擦”掉了。</span></span></span></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"margin-bottom: 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span data-eleid=\"79\" style=\"white-space: pre-wrap;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">第二层摩擦，就是架构师。你要做个库存管理系统，他让你上个Oracle数据库。Oralce数据库按CPU和连接数计价。你一听价格，吓住了。想算了。我就30个员工。还是找个老大爷负责看着每个人在领用单上签字吧。</span></span></span></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"margin-bottom: 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span data-eleid=\"81\" style=\"white-space: pre-wrap;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">但其实，他推荐Oracle，是因为你把他从大公司挖来之前，他只会用Oracle，对轻量级数据库一无所知，甚至鄙视。</span></span></span></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"margin-bottom: 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span data-eleid=\"83\" style=\"white-space: pre-wrap;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">你觉得不必要。但他一句“出了问题你不要找我”就把你怼回去了。</span></span></span></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"margin-bottom: 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span data-eleid=\"85\" style=\"white-space: pre-wrap;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">第三层摩擦，就是程序员。</span></span></span></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"margin-bottom: 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span data-eleid=\"87\" style=\"white-space: pre-wrap;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">所有的产品设计，架构设计，在过去，都要靠程序员一行一行代码写成软件系统。</span></span></span></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"margin-bottom: 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span data-eleid=\"89\" style=\"white-space: pre-wrap;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">我有41年写程序的经验。虽然离开微软，创立咨询公司也已经13年了，但一直没真正停止写代码。我们公司的财务分账工具，就是我自己写的。我太懂程序员了。</span></span></span></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"margin-bottom: 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span data-eleid=\"91\" style=\"white-space: pre-wrap;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">顺起来，不想睡觉。不顺，遇到bug，更不想睡觉。一行行代码，就像一块块砖头，没日没夜砌起高楼大厦。</span></span></span></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"margin-bottom: 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span data-eleid=\"93\" style=\"white-space: pre-wrap;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">所以程序员很贵。因此，上海相亲角的丈母娘很喜欢程序员。但也是因此有，你的系统动不动就要至少几十万，开发半年。</span></span></span></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"margin-bottom: 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span data-eleid=\"95\" style=\"white-space: pre-wrap;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">这一层高昂的成本摩擦，让很多中小企业放弃了在信息化和数字化面前，止步不前。花500万成本，换取200万的提效。还是算了吧。信息化成了大公司的专利。小公司和大公司之间的“数字鸿沟”越来越深。</span></span></span></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"margin-bottom: 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span data-eleid=\"97\" style=\"white-space: pre-wrap;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">你现在理解，为什么X、Z、和W这么激动了。因为长期以来，信息化是属于大公司的“昂贵军备”，中小企业只能在效率的泥潭里肉搏。</span></span></span></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"margin-bottom: 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span data-eleid=\"99\" style=\"white-space: pre-wrap;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">但AI编程的出现，正在抹平这道鸿沟。它把原本属于大公司的技术特权，拆解成了每个人都能握住的工具。</span></span></span></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"margin-bottom: 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span data-eleid=\"101\" style=\"line-height: 1.75em;white-space: pre-wrap;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"line-height: 1.75em;white-space: pre-wrap;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:15px;\">还是那200万的提效，但是AI编程，把成本从500万，直接降到了50万。他们突然发现，有太多以前不能做的事情多，今天突然可以做了。</span></span></span></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"margin-bottom: 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span data-eleid=\"103\" style=\"white-space: pre-wrap;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">大量被成本封印了几十年的效率优势，在2026年会突然被“AI编程”彻底引爆。</span></span></span></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"margin-bottom: 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span data-eleid=\"105\" style=\"white-space: pre-wrap;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">这一仗，拼的不再是口袋里的预算，而是大脑里的逻辑。</span></span></span></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"margin-bottom: 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span data-eleid=\"107\" style=\"white-space: pre-wrap;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">效率的闸门已经开启。</span></span></span></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"margin-bottom: 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span data-eleid=\"109\" style=\"white-space: pre-wrap;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">请尽情冲刺。</span></span></span></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"4 9 []\" style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;font-size:17px;box-sizing:border-box !important;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);outline:0px;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:justify;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px;margin:0px;letter-spacing:0.544px;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\"><span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin-top: 0px;margin-right: 0px;margin-left: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;letter-spacing: 0.578px;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin-top: 0px;margin-right: 0px;margin-left: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;letter-spacing: 0.578px;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\" data-pm-slice=\"2 4 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;data-pm-slice&quot;:&quot;3 9 []&quot;,&quot;style&quot;:&quot;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-family: \\&quot;PingFang SC\\&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \\&quot;Helvetica Neue\\&quot;, \\&quot;Hiragino Sans GB\\&quot;, \\&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI\\&quot;, \\&quot;Microsoft YaHei\\&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 17px;font-style: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;letter-spacing: 0.544px;orphans: 2;text-align: justify;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin-top: 0px;margin-right: 0px;margin-left: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 12px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);font-weight: bold;text-decoration: none;\">作者</span></span><span data-pm-slice=\"3 3 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;h2&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;data-pm-slice&quot;:&quot;4 7 []&quot;,&quot;style&quot;:&quot;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; font-weight: 400; font-size: 16px; max-width: 100%; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9); font-family: \\&quot;PingFang SC\\&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \\&quot;Helvetica Neue\\&quot;, \\&quot;Hiragino Sans GB\\&quot;, \\&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI\\&quot;, \\&quot;Microsoft YaHei\\&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: 0.544px; orphans: 2; text-align: justify; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin-top: 0px;margin-right: 0px;margin-left: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-align: left;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 12px;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin-top: 0px;margin-right: 0px;margin-left: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);letter-spacing: 0.578px;caret-color: rgb(34, 34, 34);box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin-top: 0px;margin-right: 0px;margin-left: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 12px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">/ 刘润&nbsp;</span></span></span></span></span></span><span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin-top: 0px;margin-right: 0px;margin-left: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-align: left;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 12px;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><strong style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin-top: 0px;margin-right: 0px;margin-left: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);letter-spacing: 0.578px;caret-color: rgb(34, 34, 34);box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin-top: 0px;margin-right: 0px;margin-left: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 12px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">编辑&nbsp;</span></span></strong><span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin-top: 0px;margin-right: 0px;margin-left: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);letter-spacing: 0.578px;caret-color: rgb(34, 34, 34);box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin-top: 0px;margin-right: 0px;margin-left: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 12px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">/ 歌平&nbsp;</span></span></span><strong style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin-top: 0px;margin-right: 0px;margin-left: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);letter-spacing: 0.578px;caret-color: rgb(34, 34, 34);box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin-top: 0px;margin-right: 0px;margin-left: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 12px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">版面&nbsp;</span></span></strong><span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin-top: 0px;margin-right: 0px;margin-left: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);letter-spacing: 0.578px;caret-color: rgb(34, 34, 34);box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin-top: 0px;margin-right: 0px;margin-left: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 12px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">/ 黄</span></span></span></span><span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin-top: 0px;margin-right: 0px;margin-left: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;text-align: left;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);letter-spacing: 0.578px;caret-color: rgb(34, 34, 34);font-size: 12px;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin-top: 0px;margin-right: 0px;margin-left: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 12px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">静</span></span></span></p>\n </body>\n</html>",
  "aiSummary": "刘润通过三个中小企业案例，揭示 2026 年 AI 编程将成为中小企业信息化弯道超车的大机会，可将开发成本从 500 万降至 50 万，抹平数字鸿沟。",
  "oneSentenceSummary": "刘润通过三个中小企业案例，揭示 2026 年 AI 编程将成为中小企业信息化弯道超车的大机会，可将开发成本从 500 万降至 50 万，抹平数字鸿沟。",
  "summary": "本文是刘润基于加拉帕戈斯之旅的见闻，分享了三位中小企业创业者利用 AI 编程解决信息化难题的案例。作者认为，2026 年 AI 编程将大幅降低中小企业的信息化建设成本（从数百万降至几十万），让原本属于大公司的技术特权变成人人可用的工具。文章分析了传统信息化建设中的三层摩擦（产品经理、架构师、程序员），指出 AI 编程正在抹平大企业与中小企业之间的数字鸿沟，效率的闸门已经开启。",
  "mainPoints": [
